         <div id="version130" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">
               <h4>Release Date: 2013/11/26</h4>
               <h4>New Features</h4>
               <p>
                  This release focused on cleaning up the editing workflow, especially as it applies to work items.
                  This release also added points estimates to the work items.
               </p>
               <ul>
                  <li>
                     Modifications to the editor workflow
                     <ul>
                        <li>
                           The editor has three modes
                           <ul>
                              <li>Read-Only - Base data is read-only, child data is visible and accessible</li>
                              <li>Edit - Base data is editable, child data is hidden and inaccessible</li>
                              <li>Create - Same as edit except the item is being created rather than modified</li>
                           </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                           Edit Workflow
                           <ul>
                              <li>Item loaded into editor in Read-Only mode</li>
                              <li>Press Edit to put editor in Edit mode</li>
                              <li>
                                 Possible actions upon completion of edit:
                                 <ul>
                                    <li>Done Editing - save changes to database, back to read-only mode</li>
                                    <li>Cancel - abandon any changes, back to read-only mode</li>
                                 </ul>
                              </li>
                              <li>
                                 Press Close to close the editor and go back to previous screen or press Edit
                                 to further edit the item
                              </li>
                           </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                           Create Workflow
                           <ul>
                              <li>Empty editor loads in Create mode</li>
                              <li>
                                 Possible actions upon completion of create:
                                 <ul>
                                    <li>Create - add item to database, load newly created item in read-only mode</li>
                                    <li>Cancel - abandon any creation, close the editor going back to previous screen</li>
                                 </ul>
                              </li>
                              <li>
                                 Press Close to close the editor and go back to previous screen or press Edit
                                 to further edit the newly created item
                              </li>
                           </ul>
                        </li>
                     </ul>
                  <li>
                     Added points estimates to the work items
                     <ul>
                        <li>Points must be entered for non-backlog items</li>
                        <li>
                           Points cannot be entered for backlog items since points for a backlog item
                           are the sum of the points for the child tasks
                        </li>
                        <li>Points Remaining defaults to points</li>
                        <li>Points can only be updated if the work item is in an Unstarted status</li>
                        <li>
                           Points Remaining can be updated until the work item gets a Complete status, at which
                           point Points Remaining is automatically set to zero
                        </li>
                     </ul>
                  </li>
               </ul>
               <h4>Bug Fixes</h4>
